OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778576786
OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to attempted
OL,4,Cassassination of Donald Trump
OL,6,FThe suspect in the White House dinner
OL,7,Fshooting has pleaded not guilty to the
OL,8,Fattempted assassination of US
OL,9,FPresident Donald Trump and other
OL,10,Fcharges.
OL,12,FCole Tomas Allen, 31, was accused of
OL,13,Fattending a White House
OL,14,FCorrespondents' Dinner in Washington,
OL,15,FDC, on April 26, armed with a shotgun
OL,16,Fwhile Trump was attending.
OL,18,FAllen was also accused of firing shots
OL,19,Fwhile running through a security
OL,20,Fcheckpoint.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
