OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778576786
OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to attempted
OL,4,Cassassination of Donald Trump
OL,6,FHe also pleaded not guilty on Monday
OL,7,Fto assaulting a federal police
OL,8,Fofficer, after a Secret Service agent
OL,9,Fwas shot in his protective vest and
OL,10,Fsurvived.
OL,12,FAllen allegedly sent messages to his
OL,13,Ffamily before the shooting, describing
OL,14,Fhimself as a "Friendly Federal
OL,15,FAssassin" and voiced grievances about
OL,16,Fthe actions of the US administration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
