OL,3,CMan pleads not guilty to attempted
OL,4,Cassassination of Donald Trump
OL,6,FHe is believed to have travelled by
OL,7,Ftrain from California to Chicago and
OL,8,Fthen onto Washington, where he checked
OL,9,Fhimself in as a guest at the hotel
OL,10,Fwhere the gala dinner was being held.
